CD-ROM PROVIDES DATA ON EUROPEAN FIRMS

EUROPAGES CD-ROM lists 150,000 companies in 25 European countries.  
Entries include detailed financial data, product and service 
descriptions, and complete contact information.  Paid advertising 
supplements the listings by providing even more details.
 
The multilingual CD-ROM (in English, French, German, Spanish, and 
Italian) costs 1,295 French francs from Eur dit S.A., 9 Avenue de 
Friedland, 75008 Paris, France; phone 011-33-1-5377-5409; fax 011-33-
1-4289-3473.



