<A NAME = "16"></A>Copyright
THE INTERNATIONAL INFORMATION REPORT via NewsNet
JANUARY, 1996

FREE STATISTICS FROM AUSTRIA

The new edition of the Austrian Central Statistical Office's 
(OSTAT's) FACTS & FIGURES provides a wealth of statistics, through 
1995, on topics ranging from agriculture and banking to 
transportation and tourism.
 
For a FREE copy of the 32-page pocket-size reference, contact OSTAT, 
Hintere Zollamtsstrasse 2b, 1033 Vienna, Austria; phone 011-43-1-71128; 
fax 011-43-1-715-6828.  For a list of all statistical publications, 
request a copy of the FREE catalog of publications, PUBLIKATIONSANGEBOT, 
from the same source.



