POCKET HANDBOOK OF THE RUSSIAN FAR EAST:  A REFERENCE GUIDE includes 
a survey of the entire region.  It includes statistical charts and 
tables, territorial and city maps, a hotel guide, information on 
elected officials, economic surveys, and more.
 
The GUIDE costs $37.50 from RUSSIAN FAR EAST UPDATE, P.O. Box 22126, 
