Yamazaki Baking expected to see lower pretax profit+

TOKYO, Dec. 29 Kyodo

     Yamazaki Baking Co. is expected to post an 8% fall in
unconsolidated pretax profit to 22 billion yen in the 1995 business
year ending Dec. 31 from the previous year for the second straight
year of decline, a business daily reported Friday.
     The top Japanese baking company's expected profit fall is
